Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.57,0:00:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,领 衔 主 演:  罗 伯 特 · 德 尼 罗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,领 衔 主 演:  雷 · 利 奥 塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,领 衔 主 演:  乔 · 佩 西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,领 衔 主 演:  洛 兰 · 布 蕾 科
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,领 衔 主 演:  保 罗 · 索 维 诺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本 片 改 编 自 真 实 故 事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纽约  1970年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音\N{\fs16\fsp0}What the fuck is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米\N{\fs16\fsp0}Jimmy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么事  - 我是不是撞到什么了\N{\fs16\fsp0}- What's up? - Did I hit something?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么\N{\fs16\fsp0}What the fuck is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是爆胎啦\N{\fs16\fsp0}Maybe you got a flat?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.12,0:01:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦\N{\fs16\fsp0}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妈的  最好停下来看看\N{\fs16\fsp0}What the fuck? You better pull over and see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还活着  你他妈的真是人渣\N{\fs16\fsp0}He's still alive. You fucking piece of shit!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧  婊子养的  看着我\N{\fs16\fsp0}Die, you motherfucker! Look at me!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从我有记忆开始  我就想成为黑帮分子\N{\fs16\fsp0}As far back as I can remember, I always wanted to be a gangster.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盗 亦 有 道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,监 制:  芭 芭 拉 · 德 菲 纳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本 片 改 编 自 尼 古 拉 斯 · 派 勒 吉 所 著 ‘黑 帮 兄 弟’ 一 书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,编 剧\N尼 古 拉 斯 · 派 勒 吉 & 马 丁 · 斯 科 塞 斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制 片:  艾 文 · 温 克 勒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导 演:  马 丁 · 斯 科 塞 斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说\N{\fs16\fsp0}To me,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为黑帮分子比当选美国总统还好\N{\fs16\fsp0}being a gangster was better than being president of the United States.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纽约东区  布鲁克林  1955年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我去计程车站找零工之前\N{\fs16\fsp0}Even before I first wandered into the cabstand for an after-school job...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道我要成为他们的一份子\N{\fs16\fsp0}I knew I wanted to be a part of them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有种归属感\N{\fs16\fsp0}It was there that I knew I belonged.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说是一种成就感  在一个充满了无名小卒的环境中\N{\fs16\fsp0}To me, it meant being somebody in a neighborhood full of nobodies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不像别人  他们能随心所欲\N{\fs16\fsp0}They weren't like anybody else. They did whatever they wanted.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在消防栓前面停车而从来也不会被开罚单\N{\fs16\fsp0}They double-parked in front of a hydrant, nobody ever gave them a ticket.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天通宵赌扑克\N{\fs16\fsp0}In the summer, when they played cards all night...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也没人敢叫警察\N{\fs16\fsp0}nobody ever called the cops.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东尼·史达斯  你好吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}Tony Stacks. How are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杜迪·西席罗\N{\fs16\fsp0}Tuddy Cicero.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是加拿希小子吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}Could this be the Canarsie Kid?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好吗  - 蛮好的\N{\fs16\fsp0}- How are you? - Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杜迪\N{\fs16\fsp0}Tuddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杜迪的大哥保利是整个社区的大老板\N{\fs16\fsp0}Tuddy ran the cabstand and the Bella Vista Pizzeria...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他替他打理计程车站和贝拉维斯塔披萨屋等地点\N{\fs16\fsp0}and other places for his brother, Paul, who was the boss of the neighborhood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利看起来动作很慢\N{\fs16\fsp0}Paulie might have moved slow...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为保利不需要为任何人做事\N{\fs16\fsp0}but it was only because Paulie didn't have to move for anybody.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 都是你不好  - 是你先开始的\N{\fs16\fsp0}- It's your fault. - You started it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先开始的  是你不好\N{\fs16\fsp0}I started it? It's your fault.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起先我父母都很高兴我在对街找到一份工作\N{\fs16\fsp0}At first my parents loved that I found a job across the street from the house.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲是爱尔兰人  他十一岁就被送去工作了\N{\fs16\fsp0}My father, who was Irish, was sent to work at the age of 11.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很高兴我找到工作\N{\fs16\fsp0}He liked that I got myself a job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他常说美国孩子都被惯坏了\N{\fs16\fsp0}He always used to say that American kids were spoiled lazy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 爸  再见  - 再见\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Bye, Dad. - Bye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见  米奇\N{\fs16\fsp0}See you, Mikey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见  亨利\N{\fs16\fsp0}Bye, Henry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亨利  过马路要小心呀\N{\fs16\fsp0}Henry! Watch how you cross!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得带牛奶回来\N{\fs16\fsp0}Bring back milk!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈也高兴呀  当她知道西席罗家\N{\fs16\fsp0}My mother was happy after she found out that the Ciceros...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和她是从西西里同一个地区出来的  对我妈妈而言\N{\fs16\fsp0}came from the same part of Sicily as she did. To my mother...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像她的祷告都应验了\N{\fs16\fsp0}that was the answer to all her prayers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是世上最幸运的小孩\N{\fs16\fsp0}I was the luckiest kid in the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以到任何地方  做任何事\N{\fs16\fsp0}I could go anywhere, I could do anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认识每一个人  大家也都认识我\N{\fs16\fsp0}I knew everybody, and everybody knew me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟们开车来  杜迪就让我\N{\fs16\fsp0}Wiseguys would pull up and Tuddy would toss me their keys...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮他们停凯迪拉克车\N{\fs16\fsp0}and let me park their Cadillacs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我还是个小鬼\N{\fs16\fsp0}Here I am, this little kid,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在方向盘后面  连路都看不见\N{\fs16\fsp0}I can't even see over the steering wheel...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能停凯迪拉克了\N{\fs16\fsp0}and I'm parking Cadillacs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  没多久\N{\fs16\fsp0}But it wasn't too long...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父母就反对我在计程车站的工作了\N{\fs16\fsp0}before my parents changed their minds about my job at the cabstand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你妈妈跟妹妹\N{\fs16\fsp0}For your mother and sister.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对他们来说  计程站的工作只是零工  对我\N{\fs16\fsp0}For them, the cabstand was supposed to be a part-time job. But for me...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却是全天候\N{\fs16\fsp0}it was definitely full-time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一想做的事\N{\fs16\fsp0}That's all I wanted to do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我爸爸这种人永远也不会了解  我是其中的一份子\N{\fs16\fsp0}People like my father could never understand, but I was a part of something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有所属  他们以成人待我\N{\fs16\fsp0}I belonged. I was treated like a grown-up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他519\N{\fs16\fsp0}Tell him 519.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天我都在学些有用的技巧\N{\fs16\fsp0}Every day I was learning to score.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里一块钱  那里一块钱\N{\fs16\fsp0}A dollar here, a dollar there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像活在梦幻里\N{\fs16\fsp0}I was living in a fantasy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天在学校还顺利吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}Did you have a good day at school?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲总是非常生气\N{\fs16\fsp0}My father was always pissed off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他气自己赚钱太少\N{\fs16\fsp0}Pissed that he made such lousy money...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他气弟弟米奇活在轮椅上\N{\fs16\fsp0}pissed that my kid brother Michael was in a wheelchair.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他气我们一家七口挤在一间小房子里\N{\fs16\fsp0}He was pissed that there were seven of us living in such a tiny house.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我说说这个\N{\fs16\fsp0}Tell me about this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是学校来的信\N{\fs16\fsp0}It's a letter from school.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信上说你已经几个月没上学了\N{\fs16\fsp0}It says you haven't been there in months.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几个月了\N{\fs16\fsp0}In months!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个没用的混球\N{\fs16\fsp0}You're a bum!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你长大想做个流浪汉吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}Want to grow up to be a bum?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过了一阵子之后  他气我整天泡在计程车站\N{\fs16\fsp0}After a while, he was mostly pissed because I hung around the cabstand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他知道站里有些什么勾当\N{\fs16\fsp0}He knew what went on at that cabstand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我经常挨揍  可是我已经不在乎了\N{\fs16\fsp0}Every once in a while, I'd have to take a beating. But by then, I didn't care.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就我看来\N{\fs16\fsp0}The way I saw it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都有挨揍的时候\N{\fs16\fsp0}everybody takes a beating sometime.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不能再送货了  - 什么  你这样会把所有事都搞砸\N{\fs16\fsp0}- I can't make any more deliveries. - What? You'll fuck everything up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老爸说他会杀了我  你看\N{\fs16\fsp0}My dad says he'll kill me. Look.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\N{\fs16\fsp0}Come on with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是送信到你家的邮差吗  - 不是\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Is that him, kid? - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那一个呢  - 也不是\N{\fs16\fsp0}- How about him? - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那个就是  - 去找他\N{\fs16\fsp0}- That's the guy. - Get him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fs16\fsp0}Excuse me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 人渣  - 你这块狗屎  给我过来\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Scumbag. - Come here, you piece of shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 认识这个小鬼吗  - 认得呀\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Know this kid? - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你知道他住哪里吗  - 知道\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Know where he lives? - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这家的信是由你送的吗  - 是的\N{\fs16\fsp0}- You deliver mail to his house? - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起  任何从学校寄给他家的信都给我\N{\fs16\fsp0}From now on, any letter from that school to his house comes directly here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你懂吗  - 懂\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Understand? - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如再有一封学校的信送进那小鬼家里的话\N{\fs16\fsp0}Another letter from that school goes to that kid's house...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会被塞进烤披萨的炉子里\N{\fs16\fsp0}in the fucking oven you'll go, head first.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  再也没有缺课的来信  再也没有学校的来信\N{\fs16\fsp0}That was it. No more letters from truant officers. No letters from school.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实  任何信件都没有了\N{\fs16\fsp0}In fact, no more letters from anybody.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后  经过几星期  我妈妈去邮局抱怨了\N{\fs16\fsp0}Finally after a few weeks, my mother went to the post office to complain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后  我怎么能回到学校去发誓效忠国旗\N{\fs16\fsp0}How could I go to school after that...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又怎能坐在那里听政府如何好的屁话呢\N{\fs16\fsp0}and pledge allegiance to the flag and sit through good government bullshit?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利最恨电话了  他不肯在家里装电话\N{\fs16\fsp0}Paulie hated phones. He wouldn't have one in his house.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米奇打来了  要不要我回他电话\N{\fs16\fsp0}Mickey called. Want me to call him back?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  打过去\N{\fs16\fsp0}All right, make the call.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的电话都是由别人传达给他\N{\fs16\fsp0}He got all his calls second hand. Then you'd have to call the people back...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后手下再从公用电话回电\N{\fs16\fsp0}from an outside phone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有五分钱  帮我打个电话给他\N{\fs16\fsp0}Got a nickel? Get him on the phone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有几个混混整天就是忙着帮保利接电话\N{\fs16\fsp0}There were guys, that's all they did all day, was take care of Paulie's calls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对一个整天忙碌不停的人来说  他很少跟人说话\N{\fs16\fsp0}For a guy who moved all day long, Paulie didn't talk to six people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如工会有了问题或彩票上有争议\N{\fs16\fsp0}If there was a union problem or, say, a beef in the numbers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有高级干部可以跟保利商议\N{\fs16\fsp0}only the top guys could meet with Paulie to discuss the problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利讨厌开会  凡事都是一对一解决\N{\fs16\fsp0}Everything was one-on-one. Paulie hated conferences.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不要别人听到他说的话\N{\fs16\fsp0}He didn't want anybody hearing what he said...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或听到别人说给他听的话\N{\fs16\fsp0}and he didn't want anybody listening to what he was being told.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好几百人以保利当靠山  他们所赚的都给保利一份\N{\fs16\fsp0}Hundreds of guys depended on Paulie, he got a piece of everything they made.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是保护费  就像在西西里  只不过这是美国\N{\fs16\fsp0}It was a tribute, like in the old country, except they were doing it in America.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利也只不过保护他们不被别人欺侮诈骗\N{\fs16\fsp0}All they got from Paulie was protection from other guys looking to rip them off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  FBI始终搞不懂这一点\N{\fs16\fsp0}That's what it's all about. That's what the FBI could never understand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利所做的\N{\fs16\fsp0}What Paulie and the Organization does...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是保护那些无法受警察保护的人\N{\fs16\fsp0}is offer protection for people who can't go to the cops. That's it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利就像是兄弟们的警察局长\N{\fs16\fsp0}That's all it is. They're like the police department for wiseguys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别人看我的眼光都不一样  因为我和大人物在一起\N{\fs16\fsp0}People looked at me differently, and they knew I was with somebody.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我连礼拜天买新鲜面包都用不着排队了\N{\fs16\fsp0}I didn't have to wait in line at the bakery on Sunday mornings for fresh bread.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老板知道我跟谁在一起\N{\fs16\fsp0}The owner knew who I was with...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会从柜台后面走出来  不管有多少人在等\N{\fs16\fsp0}and he'd come from around the counter. No matter how many were waiting...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他都会先招呼我\N{\fs16\fsp0}I was taken care of first.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邻居再也不将车停在我们车道上了\N{\fs16\fsp0}Our neighbors didn't park in our driveway anymore...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们没有车  我十三岁的时候\N{\fs16\fsp0}even though we didn't have a car. At 13...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我赚的钱已经比附近的大人还多\N{\fs16\fsp0}I was making more money than most of the grown-ups around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的钱多得花不完  要什么有什么\N{\fs16\fsp0}I had more money than I could spend. I had it all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天  附近几个孩子们还帮我妈把菜拎回家\N{\fs16\fsp0}One day, some neighborhood kids carried my mother's groceries all the way home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道为什么吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}You know why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们尊敬我\N{\fs16\fsp0}It was out of respect.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  你认为如何\N{\fs16\fsp0}Hi, Mom, what do you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你看我的鞋  很棒吧  - 老天呀\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Look at my shoes, aren't they great? - My God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看上去像个黑帮分子\N{\fs16\fsp0}You look like a gangster.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们射中我了  救命\N{\fs16\fsp0}They shot me. Help!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亨利  把门关上\N{\fs16\fsp0}Henry, shut the door.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我第一次看到枪击\N{\fs16\fsp0}That was the first time I had ever seen anyone shot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别在店里搞这些  天呐\N{\fs16\fsp0}Can't have that in here. Jesus Christ!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不准在这里弄这种事\N{\fs16\fsp0}I can't have that in this joint.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得我为那个人感到难过\N{\fs16\fsp0}I remember feeling bad about the guy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也记得或许杜迪是对的\N{\fs16\fsp0}but I also remember feeling that maybe Tuddy was right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道保利不要有任何人死在屋里\N{\fs16\fsp0}I knew Paulie didn't want anybody dying in the building.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个大白痴  你糟蹋了八条围裙\N{\fs16\fsp0}You're a real jerk. You wasted eight fucking aprons on this guy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他妈的到底怎么了  我要让这个小鬼长进一点\N{\fs16\fsp0}What the hell's wrong with you? I got to toughen this kid up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是一段光彩的日子\N{\fs16\fsp0}It was a glorious time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是兄弟们\N{\fs16\fsp0}And wiseguys were all over the place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在阿帕拉钦事件之前\N{\fs16\fsp0}It was before Apalachin and before Crazy Joe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在疯子周和老大开战前\N{\fs16\fsp0}decided to take on a boss and start a war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是那时候认清世界\N{\fs16\fsp0}It was when I met the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并认识吉米·康威\N{\fs16\fsp0}And it was when I first met Jimmy Conway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他顶多不过二十八九岁\N{\fs16\fsp0}He couldn't have been more than 28 or 29 at the time...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但已经是个传奇人物了\N{\fs16\fsp0}but he was already a legend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只要一走进来  厅里所有的人就像发疯一样\N{\fs16\fsp0}He'd walk in the door and everybody who worked the room just went wild.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮他开门  就给一百块小费\N{\fs16\fsp0}He'd give the doorman $100 just for opening the door.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他常塞百元大钞给那些发牌跟主持赌局的人\N{\fs16\fsp0}He'd give hundreds to the dealers and the guys who ran the games.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连酒保也有百元小费  只要冰块够冰的话\N{\fs16\fsp0}The bartender got $100 just for keeping the ice cubes cold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让爱尔兰人来赢你们这些意大利人的钱了\N{\fs16\fsp0}The Irishman is here to take all you guineas' money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要不要喝一杯  - 给我一杯七喜加海马七威士忌\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Want a drink? - Give me a 7 and 7.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 来见见这个小子亨利  - 很高兴认识你\N{\fs16\fsp0}- I'd like you to meet the kid Henry. - How you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢你  - 继续上酒\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Thank you. - Keep them coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米是全城当时最令人敬畏的人之一\N{\fs16\fsp0}Jimmy was one of the most feared guys in the city.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他第一次被关起来时才十一岁\N{\fs16\fsp0}He was first locked up at 11...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十六岁就替他老板杀人了\N{\fs16\fsp0}and he was doing hits for mob bosses when he was 16.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米一点也不在乎杀人  那是他的职业\N{\fs16\fsp0}See, hits never bothered Jimmy. It was business.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是吉米真正的爱好\N{\fs16\fsp0}But what Jimmy really loved to do...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是偷东西\N{\fs16\fsp0}what he really loved to do was steal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那对他来说是一种享受\N{\fs16\fsp0}He actually enjoyed it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米就是那种支持电影里的坏蛋的那种人\N{\fs16\fsp0}Jimmy was the kind of guy who rooted for the bad guys in the movies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的钱包给我\N{\fs16\fsp0}Give me your wallet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也许知道我们是谁  我们可清楚的知道你的底细  懂吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}You might know who we are, but we know who you are. Understand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是当时城里最大的劫车犯之一\N{\fs16\fsp0}He was one of the city's biggest hijackers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劫运酒车  运烟车  运虾  刮胡刀  龙虾等等\N{\fs16\fsp0}of booze, cigarettes, razor blades, shrimp and lobsters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虾跟龙虾是最好的货  很快就销出去了\N{\fs16\fsp0}Shrimp and lobsters were best. They went really fast.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几乎所有的劫案都是不用暴力的\N{\fs16\fsp0}Almost all of them were gimmies. They just gave it up, no problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们甚至称他为绅士吉米\N{\fs16\fsp0}They called him Jimmy the Gent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮小姐\N{\fs16\fsp0}Help the lady.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开货车的都喜欢他  有好货的时候\N{\fs16\fsp0}Drivers loved him. They used to tip him off...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:13:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都会把消息告诉他  当然  每个人都得到好处\N{\fs16\fsp0}about the really good loads. Of course, everybody got a piece.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢了  我等下再来拿剩下的烟\N{\fs16\fsp0}Thanks, I'll be back for the rest later.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  一会儿见\N{\fs16\fsp0}Okay, see you later.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亨利  到这里来\N{\fs16\fsp0}Henry, come here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 跟汤米打个招呼  - 你好吗  亨利\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Say hello to Tommy. - How're you doing, Henry?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们好好的一起工作  好吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}You're gonna be working together, okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管帮他\N{\fs16\fsp0}Help him. Go ahead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米  偷到什么好东西了吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}Jimmy, you got anything good?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察曾经派出大军来捉吉米  他怎么做\N{\fs16\fsp0}And when the cops assigned a whole army to stop Jimmy, what did he do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把他们变成了同伙\N{\fs16\fsp0}He made them partners.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想抱怨也没人会听\N{\fs16\fsp0}I'd complain, but who'd listen?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 一条帕尔玛尔  - 来\N{\fs16\fsp0}- One Pall Mall. - There you go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要什么  - 我要两条幸运红圈\N{\fs16\fsp0}- What do you need? - Two Luckies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 来  亨利  - 真多谢  要什么\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Here you go, Henry. - Thanks a lot... What do you need?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 一条帕尔玛尔  - 一条帕尔玛尔  来\N{\fs16\fsp0}- One Pall Mall. - One Pall Mall, here you go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你干什么  - 没有  没什么事\N{\fs16\fsp0}- What are you doing? - It's all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你有你妈的许可吗  - 你要几条烟呀\N{\fs16\fsp0}- You have permission from your mother? - How many cartons you need?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你从哪里弄来的香烟  - 把他弄走\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Where'd you get the cigarettes? - Get him out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没关系的  - 有关系\N{\fs16\fsp0}- It's okay. - It's not okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不明白  - 是你不明白  店关了\N{\fs16\fsp0}- You don't understand. - You don't understand. Store's closed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 亨利被捕了  - 在哪被捕\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Henry got pinched. - Where?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在工厂那里  他在卖烟\N{\fs16\fsp0}By the factory, selling cigarettes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亨利·希尔  纽约州控诉亨利·希尔\N{\fs16\fsp0}Henry Hill. The People of the State of New York vs. Henry Hill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案号704162\N{\fs16\fsp0}Docket number 704162.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  法官  我就是\N{\fs16\fsp0}Yes, sir. That's me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走过来  站在那别动\N{\fs16\fsp0}Just stand there. Now stay there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,律师  继续吧\N{\fs16\fsp0}Counselor, proceed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜\N{\fs16\fsp0}Congratulations.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的毕业礼物\N{\fs16\fsp0}Here's your graduation present.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么  我被捕了  - 每个人都会被捕  但你表现得很好\N{\fs16\fsp0}- What for? I got pinched. - Everyone does, but you did it right.{\r}
