Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.25,0:27:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想你可以当她女朋友的伴\N{\fs16\fsp0}So you come along, go out with her girlfriend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.39,0:28:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  我就知道\N{\fs16\fsp0}See? I knew it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.39,0:28:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么  有什么不好\N{\fs16\fsp0}You knew what? What the fuck is wrong with that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.86,0:28:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么时候  - 明天晚上\N{\fs16\fsp0}- When is this? - Tomorrow night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.06,0:28:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明晚不行  我要见杜迪\N{\fs16\fsp0}I can't, I gotta meet Tuddy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.76,0:28:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以早点出来  事后再去见杜迪\N{\fs16\fsp0}You could meet Tuddy. You can come early and then still go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.67,0:28:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你怎么老是这样  - 别找理由了\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Why do you always do this? - Don't give me that shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.17,0:28:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是找你帮忙\N{\fs16\fsp0}What did I ask you for? I'm asking you for a favor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.80,0:28:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮过你不少忙的\N{\fs16\fsp0}I do a lot of fucking favors for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.77,0:28:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想搞那娘们  你懂不懂\N{\fs16\fsp0}I'm trying to bang this fucking broad. Help me out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.51,0:28:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真的很漂亮\N{\fs16\fsp0}I don't understand you. She's beautiful!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.05,0:28:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住在高级区  这些犹太女孩很有钱\N{\fs16\fsp0}Her fucking family lives in the Five Towns. These Jews got money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.28,0:28:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定整条街都是她家的  你也许会中头奖也不一定\N{\fs16\fsp0}Maybe the family owns the whole block. You may wind up with a big score.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.72,0:28:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光听你讲犹太女朋友好了\N{\fs16\fsp0}You with your fucking mouth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.26,0:28:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我约了杜迪十一点见  现在我正在给汤米做搭档\N{\fs16\fsp0}I had a meeting with Tuddy at 11:00, and here I am, a backup guy for Tommy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.10,0:28:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吃饱了吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}How about it? Did you have enough to eat?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.60,0:28:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃  我正在节食\N{\fs16\fsp0}It was delicious. I'm just watching my diet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.31,0:28:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我替你注意身材就好了\N{\fs16\fsp0}Let me watch your figure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.81,0:28:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等不及离开\N{\fs16\fsp0}I couldn't wait to get away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.51,0:28:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还在吃主菜  我就已经叫点心了\N{\fs16\fsp0}I was ordering the dessert when they were eating dinner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.24,0:28:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还在喝咖啡  我就先结帐了\N{\fs16\fsp0}When they were having coffee, I was asking for a check.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.88,0:29:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有事情\N{\fs16\fsp0}I had business.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.25,0:29:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝点咖啡吧  会清醒一点\N{\fs16\fsp0}Have some coffee. It'll wake you up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.05,0:29:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 帐单给我  - 你急什么呀\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Can we have the check? - What are you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.19,0:29:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我得走了  - 我们才刚到\N{\fs16\fsp0}- I got to go. - We just got here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.49,0:29:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事  我要走了\N{\fs16\fsp0}I got that thing. I gotta go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.69,0:29:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再等几分钟  我们一起离开好吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}Wait a couple of minutes. We'll leave together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.96,0:29:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样才不会像一群流浪汉  一个一个走\N{\fs16\fsp0}This way we don't go out like a bunch of hobos, one at a time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.37,0:29:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了他\N{\fs16\fsp0}I couldn't stand him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.47,0:29:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得他真的很倒胃口\N{\fs16\fsp0}I thought he was really obnoxious.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.84,0:29:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四肢一直摆弄着\N{\fs16\fsp0}He kept fidgeting around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.87,0:29:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以不要玩打火机  很烦\N{\fs16\fsp0}You don't mind, do you? That's very annoying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.35,0:29:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许甜酒比较适合你  但我喝就不像样了\N{\fs16\fsp0}Good? You might prefer Manischewitz, but it'd look funny on my table.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.52,0:29:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可以走了吧  - 亨利  放松一点嘛\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Ready? - Henry, lighten up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.06,0:29:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们才刚到  别紧张  好不好\N{\fs16\fsp0}We just got here. What are you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.33,0:29:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回家的时候还没到  他就把我推进车门\N{\fs16\fsp0}Before it was time to go home, he was pushing me into the car...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.86,0:29:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又拉了出来  太荒唐了\N{\fs16\fsp0}then pulling me out. It was ridiculous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.93,0:29:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴安和汤米\N{\fs16\fsp0}Diane and Tommy made us promise...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.24,0:29:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又约我们星期五见\N{\fs16\fsp0}to meet them again on Friday night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.30,0:29:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们答应了\N{\fs16\fsp0}We agreed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.64,0:30:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果不其然  星期五晚上亨利没来\N{\fs16\fsp0}Of course, when Friday night came around, Henry stood me up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.48,0:30:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉  我不知道他在哪\N{\fs16\fsp0}I feel terrible. I don't know where he is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.88,0:30:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他真的很喜欢你  他一直不停地谈她\N{\fs16\fsp0}He really liked you, too. All he did was talk about her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.98,0:30:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天约会之夜只有我们三个人\N{\fs16\fsp0}We were a trio instead of a double date that night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.62,0:30:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他该来通电话  我真担心  希望不是太严重\N{\fs16\fsp0}He would have called. I hope it's nothing serious.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.62,0:30:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我逼汤米带我去找他\N{\fs16\fsp0}But I made Tommy take me looking for him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.76,0:30:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤米  你搞什么\N{\fs16\fsp0}Tommy, what the fuck?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.60,0:30:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真有种呀  跟我爽约\N{\fs16\fsp0}You got some nerve standing me up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.57,0:30:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有人敢这样对我\N{\fs16\fsp0}Nobody does that to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.13,0:30:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你是谁  像法兰奇·瓦利那样的大歌星吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}Who do you think you are, Frankie Valli or some kind of big shot?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.84,0:30:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着好不好  我忘了  我以为是下星期\N{\fs16\fsp0}Slow down, I forgot. I thought it was next week.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.01,0:30:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这个星期五  你答应的  你这个骗子\N{\fs16\fsp0}It was this Friday and you agreed, so you're a liar!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.31,0:30:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  别这样  我们好好谈一下\N{\fs16\fsp0}We can talk about this. Take it easy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.38,0:30:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好谈的\N{\fs16\fsp0}Talk about it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.98,0:30:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去你的吧  我们没什么好谈的\N{\fs16\fsp0}Talk to you after what you just did to me? Forget it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.82,0:30:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你不会来的  你那天什么也不说  一副无聊的样子\N{\fs16\fsp0}I thought you would stand me up. You looked bored. You didn't say anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.69,0:30:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再给我一次补偿的机会吧\N{\fs16\fsp0}Let me make it up to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.96,0:30:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我考虑一下\N{\fs16\fsp0}I'll think about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.33,0:30:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得她在街上大喊大叫\N{\fs16\fsp0}I remember, she was screaming on the street, and I mean loud.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.04,0:31:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是看起来真动人\N{\fs16\fsp0}But she looked good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.44,0:31:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会考虑考虑  不过有代价的  希尔\N{\fs16\fsp0}I'll think about it. But it'll cost you, Hill. A lot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.84,0:31:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的眼睛真美  就像伊莉莎白·泰勒（好莱坞女星）一样\N{\fs16\fsp0}She had these great eyes just like Liz Taylor's.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.61,0:31:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少我这么觉得\N{\fs16\fsp0}At least that's what I thought.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.08,0:31:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗  亨利\N{\fs16\fsp0}Hello, Henry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.35,0:31:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你准备好了吗  - 好了\N{\fs16\fsp0}- You're ready? - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.85,0:31:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧\N{\fs16\fsp0}Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.02,0:31:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不  等一下  - 什么\N{\fs16\fsp0}- No, wait a minute. - What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.99,0:31:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快  把十字架盖起来  我妈看到她会认为你是基督徒（犹太人不信基督教）\N{\fs16\fsp0}Quick, you have to cover that cross. My mother sees that...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.96,0:31:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯伦\N{\fs16\fsp0}Karen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.72,0:31:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈\N{\fs16\fsp0}Mom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.02,0:31:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是我朋友亨利·希尔  - 你好吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}- I'd like you to meet my friend, Henry Hill. - How do you do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.43,0:31:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿说你是半个犹太人\N{\fs16\fsp0}My daughter says that you're half Jewish.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.50,0:31:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的一半是\N{\fs16\fsp0}It's just the good half.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.20,0:31:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢  先生  - 谢谢\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Thank you, sir. - Bye, see you later, thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.40,0:31:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛把车停在这里\N{\fs16\fsp0}What're you doing? You're leaving your car?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.81,0:31:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会替我看着\N{\fs16\fsp0}He watches the car for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.64,0:31:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比停在停车场快多了\N{\fs16\fsp0}It's easier than leaving it at a garage and waiting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.54,0:31:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样快多了  懂我意思吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}It's a lot quicker that way, you know what I mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.22,0:31:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢从这里走  比排队好\N{\fs16\fsp0}I like going in this way. It's better than waiting in line.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.40,0:32:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  一切都好吧  这给你\N{\fs16\fsp0}How are you doing? What's up? Here you go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.37,0:32:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好吗  - 你好\N{\fs16\fsp0}- How are you doing? - I'm doing all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.05,0:32:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每次来  你们两个都在这里  不用工作吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}Every time I come here, every time, you two. Don't you work?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.67,0:33:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗  嗨  你好吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}Henry, nice to see you. Hi, how are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.90,0:33:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼  摆在最前面\N{\fs16\fsp0}Anthony, right in the front.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.14,0:33:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果需要什么  告诉我就好了\N{\fs16\fsp0}Anything you need, just let me know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.76,0:33:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东尼  真是谢了  我很感激\N{\fs16\fsp0}Tony, thanks a lot. I appreciate it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.44,0:33:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你给他们每人二十块钱  - 没关系的\N{\fs16\fsp0}- You gave them $20 each. - It's all right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.17,0:33:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亨利  这是东尼先生送的\N{\fs16\fsp0}Henry, this is with Mr. Tony, over there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.74,0:33:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 在哪里  - 就在这边\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Where? - Over there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.21,0:33:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢了  东尼\N{\fs16\fsp0}Thanks a lot, Tony.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.55,0:34:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你靠什么生活  - 什么\N{\fs16\fsp0}- What do you do? - What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.98,0:34:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你靠什么生活  - 我在建筑界\N{\fs16\fsp0}- What do you do? - I'm in construction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.49,0:34:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这双手不像做建筑的\N{\fs16\fsp0}They don't feel like you're in construction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.03,0:34:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是工会代表\N{\fs16\fsp0}I'm a union delegate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.23,0:34:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位女士  先生\N{\fs16\fsp0}Now, ladies and gentlemen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.90,0:34:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很荣幸为各位介绍单句笑话之王\N{\fs16\fsp0}the Copacabana is proud to present the king of one-liners...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.67,0:34:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亨利·洋曼\N{\fs16\fsp0}Henny Youngman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.71,0:34:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位好  我能在这里表演感到骄傲  请把我太太带走\N{\fs16\fsp0}How are you all? I'm glad to be here. Take my wife, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.62,0:34:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论我把我太太丢在什么地方  她总会回家\N{\fs16\fsp0}I take my wife everywhere but she finds her way home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.75,0:34:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问她要去哪里庆祝结婚纪念\N{\fs16\fsp0}I said, "Where do you wanna go for our anniversary?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.19,0:34:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说要到一个她从来没去过的地方\N{\fs16\fsp0}She said, "Somewhere I've never been before."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.22,0:34:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说  那就去厨房好了\N{\fs16\fsp0}I said, "Try the kitchen."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.66,0:34:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦士勒医生在场\N{\fs16\fsp0}Dr. Wellsler is here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.96,0:34:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给病人估计还能活六个月  时候到了却缴不出来医药费\N{\fs16\fsp0}Gave a guy six months to live. Couldn't pay his bill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.17,0:34:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他又告诉病人还能再活六个月\N{\fs16\fsp0}Gave him another six months.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.24,0:34:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真喜欢你们\N{\fs16\fsp0}I love this crowd.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.68,0:35:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非工作人员止步
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.55,0:35:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是法国航空让我成功的\N{\fs16\fsp0}Air France made me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.66,0:35:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连枪都没有用就抢走了42万\N{\fs16\fsp0}We walked out with $420,000 without using a gun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.59,0:35:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然也给了保利他应得的保护费\N{\fs16\fsp0}And we did the right thing. We gave Paulie his tribute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.70,0:35:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6万元\N{\fs16\fsp0}$60,000.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.54,0:35:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会过一个好夏天\N{\fs16\fsp0}It's going to be a good summer.{\r}
