Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.38,1:50:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会喜欢他  他是好兄弟  是我们一伙的\N{\fs16\fsp0}"You'll like this guy. He's all right. He's a goodfella, one of us."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.95,1:50:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}You understand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.99,1:50:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是好兄弟\N{\fs16\fsp0}We were goodfellas. Wiseguys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.79,1:50:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米和我都因为有爱尔兰血统  而不能被引荐\N{\fs16\fsp0}But Jimmy and I could never be made because we had Irish blood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.33,1:50:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便我母亲是西西里人也没有用\N{\fs16\fsp0}It didn't matter my mother was Sicilian.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.03,1:50:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要百分之百意大利血统才能被正式引荐\N{\fs16\fsp0}To become a member of a crew, you've got to be 100% Italian...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.14,1:50:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要能追踪出你所有亲戚的来历\N{\fs16\fsp0}so they can trace your relatives back to the old country.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.58,1:50:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是最高的荣誉\N{\fs16\fsp0}It's the highest honor they can give you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.98,1:50:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,象征你已属于一个家庭  一个团体\N{\fs16\fsp0}It means you belong to a family and a crew.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.85,1:50:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那意谓着再没有人敢伤害你\N{\fs16\fsp0}It means nobody can fuck around with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.92,1:50:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你却可以任意欺侮\N{\fs16\fsp0}It also means you could fuck around with anybody...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.49,1:50:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些不属于任何家族的人\N{\fs16\fsp0}just as long as they aren't also a member.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.10,1:50:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像拥有偷劫的执照  做任何事的执照\N{\fs16\fsp0}It's like a license to steal. A license to do anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.70,1:50:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被正式引荐有多少年了\N{\fs16\fsp0}How many years ago since you were made?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.87,1:51:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我是老人了  30年前  - 30年前呀\N{\fs16\fsp0}- I'm an old-timer. 30 years ago. - Thirty years?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.77,1:51:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  有很多值得回忆的事呀\N{\fs16\fsp0}Brings back a lot of memories.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.51,1:51:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派克山当时也只不过一粒青春痘嘛\N{\fs16\fsp0}Pike's Peak was a pimple then, wasn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.31,1:51:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吉米来说  汤米被引荐\N{\fs16\fsp0}As far as Jimmy was concerned, with Tommy being made...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.45,1:51:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像我们都被引荐了一样\N{\fs16\fsp0}it was like we were all being made.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.72,1:51:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们之中有人当了会员了\N{\fs16\fsp0}We would now have one of our own as a member.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.24,1:51:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是谁  - 是韦力\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Who's this? - This is Vinnie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.04,1:51:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  仪式完成了吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}Vinnie. What happened? Did we get straightened out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.01,1:51:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生一点问题  我们尽力了\N{\fs16\fsp0}No, we had a problem. We tried to do everything we could.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.21,1:51:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么意思\N{\fs16\fsp0}What do you mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.38,1:51:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说他死了  我们也无能为力\N{\fs16\fsp0}You know what I mean. He's gone, and we couldn't do nothing about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.42,1:51:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就这样  - 你是什么意思\N{\fs16\fsp0}- That's it. - What do you mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.46,1:51:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他死了\N{\fs16\fsp0}He's gone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.79,1:51:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样\N{\fs16\fsp0}That's it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.73,1:52:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道会这样  狗娘养的  我不能相信\N{\fs16\fsp0}I knew it! I can't fucking believe it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.95,1:52:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事啦\N{\fs16\fsp0}What happened?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.25,1:52:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们干掉他了  - 操\N{\fs16\fsp0}- They fucking whacked him - Fuck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.23,1:52:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}Are you all right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.97,1:52:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是替比利·贝兹报仇\N{\fs16\fsp0}It was revenge for Billy Batts...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.64,1:52:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一些旧的积怨\N{\fs16\fsp0}and a lot of other things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.71,1:52:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样\N{\fs16\fsp0}And that's that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.88,1:52:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一点办法也没有\N{\fs16\fsp0}There was nothing we could do about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.45,1:52:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝兹是黑手党的  汤米还不是\N{\fs16\fsp0}Batts was a made man and Tommy wasn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.65,1:52:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是老老实实的逆来顺受\N{\fs16\fsp0}We had to sit still and take it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.75,1:52:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意大利人圈子就是这样  一种毫无道理的规定\N{\fs16\fsp0}It was among the Italians. It was real greaseball shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.84,1:53:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们甚至打在汤米脸上\N{\fs16\fsp0}They even shot Tommy in the face...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.84,1:53:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他妈妈不能给他开棺瞻仰\N{\fs16\fsp0}so his mother couldn't give him an open coffin at the funeral.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.88,1:53:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1980年5月11日  星期日  上午6点55分
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.79,1:54:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来预备好要忙一整天的\N{\fs16\fsp0}I was gonna be busy all day. I had to drop off some guns at Jimmy's...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.79,1:54:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要拿枪去给吉米配消音器\N{\fs16\fsp0}to match some silencers he had.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.16,1:54:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去医院接我弟弟  带他回家吃晚饭\N{\fs16\fsp0}I had to pick up my brother at the hospital and drive him home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.36,1:54:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后去取匹兹堡来的货\N{\fs16\fsp0}I had to pick up some new Pittsburgh stuff for Lois...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.03,1:54:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给露易丝  让她将货空运给亚特兰大附近的客人\N{\fs16\fsp0}to fly down to some customers I had near Atlanta.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.48,1:54:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就知道他不会要那些枪  我知道我的钱泡汤了\N{\fs16\fsp0}Right away, I knew he didn't want them, and I'd be stuck for the money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.12,1:54:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他要我才买的  现在他又不要了\N{\fs16\fsp0}I only bought them because he wanted them, and now he didn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.56,1:54:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些有什么鬼用  一个都配不上  你在搞什么\N{\fs16\fsp0}What good are these? None of them fit. What's the matter with you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.19,1:54:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不付钱呢\N{\fs16\fsp0}I'm not paying for it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.69,1:54:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一句话也没讲  吉米气得连再见都没说\N{\fs16\fsp0}I didn't say a thing. Jimmy was so pissed off, he didn't even say goodbye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.53,1:54:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再吸毒了  你的脑子都快不管用了\N{\fs16\fsp0}Stop the drugs. They're making your mind into mush!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.13,1:54:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 听见没有  - 我把它们带回去就是了\N{\fs16\fsp0}- You hear me? - I'll take them back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.64,1:54:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上午8点05分
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.95,1:55:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些匹兹堡家伙  总是在买枪\N{\fs16\fsp0}My Pittsburgh guys always wanted guns.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.08,1:55:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我下午反正要去见他们  去取货\N{\fs16\fsp0}Since I would see them in the afternoon to pick up a delivery...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.86,1:55:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我蛮肯定我能赚回本的\N{\fs16\fsp0}I was pretty sure I'd get my money back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.41,1:55:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的老天呀\N{\fs16\fsp0}Oh, my God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.85,1:55:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上午8点45分
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.65,1:55:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我终于到了医院接麦可  医生说我该住院了\N{\fs16\fsp0}When I finally got to the hospital, Michael's doctor wanted to put me in bed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.48,1:55:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝呀  你发生什么事了\N{\fs16\fsp0}Jesus Christ, what happened to you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.65,1:55:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才差点撞车\N{\fs16\fsp0}I almost got into an accident on the way here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.19,1:55:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我描述了车祸  又说昨夜狂欢没睡\N{\fs16\fsp0}And I told him I was partying all night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.26,1:55:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我没事  - 好啦  到这边来\N{\fs16\fsp0}- I'm fine. - Come on. Get over here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.23,1:55:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 医师  我没事  - 我给你做个检查\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Doc, I'm fine. - Let me check you out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.83,1:55:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦\N{\fs16\fsp0}Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.03,1:55:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很同情我  只给了我10毫克镇静剂\N{\fs16\fsp0}He took mercy on me, gave me 10 milligrams of Valium...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.87,1:55:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让我回去了\N{\fs16\fsp0}and sent me home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.74,1:56:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我计划把弟弟送回家  同时把凯伦接上\N{\fs16\fsp0}My plan was to drop off my brother at the house and pick up Karen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.44,1:56:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看见没有  一架直升机\N{\fs16\fsp0}There it is. You see that helicopter right there?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.85,1:56:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在我们前面  它跟了我一早上了\N{\fs16\fsp0}Right in front of us, there. I think it's been following me all morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.52,1:56:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别瞎扯了  它跟踪你干什么  - 我告诉你\N{\fs16\fsp0}- Get the fuck out. What are you, nuts? - I'm telling you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.35,1:56:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道是怎么回事\N{\fs16\fsp0}I don't know what's going on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.72,1:56:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我第三次看到它  我去医院接你也看到了\N{\fs16\fsp0}It's the third time I've seen it. At the hospital I saw it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.93,1:56:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中途停了两次  每次都看到它\N{\fs16\fsp0}I had to make some stops. I've seen it every time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.63,1:56:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跑了好多地方  整天都看到它\N{\fs16\fsp0}I've been all over town and I've seen it all day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.87,1:56:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天由我做晚餐\N{\fs16\fsp0}I was cooking dinner that night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.87,1:56:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}上午11点30分
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.77,1:56:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须把肉汁熬出来做蕃茄配料\N{\fs16\fsp0}I had to start braising the beef and veal shanks for the tomato sauce.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.95,1:56:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是麦可最喜欢的菜  我做了肉酱\N{\fs16\fsp0}It was Michael's favorite. I was making ziti with meat gravy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.35,1:56:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还打算烤辣椒\N{\fs16\fsp0}and I'm planning to roast some peppers over the flames...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.02,1:56:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,橄榄油豆  大蒜等\N{\fs16\fsp0}put on some string beans with olive oil. I had some beautiful cutlets...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.12,1:56:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有切得很好的小牛肉\N{\fs16\fsp0}that were cut just right...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.36,1:56:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算炸好了当开胃菜\N{\fs16\fsp0}that I was going to fry up as an appetizer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.56,1:56:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在家停留了约一小时\N{\fs16\fsp0}So, I was home for about an hour.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.73,1:57:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我计划提早吃晚饭\N{\fs16\fsp0}My plan was to start the dinner early...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.87,1:57:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯伦和我可以把枪推销掉\N{\fs16\fsp0}so Karen and I could unload the guns Jimmy didn't want...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.57,1:57:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时把货取回来给露易丝\N{\fs16\fsp0}then get the package for Lois...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.14,1:57:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由她跑一趟亚特兰大\N{\fs16\fsp0}to take to Atlanta for her trip later that night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.57,1:57:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不时从窗户看出去  直升机已经不在了\N{\fs16\fsp0}I kept looking out the window, and I saw that the helicopter was gone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.98,1:57:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦可  注意蕃茄汁好吗  你留在这里陪麦可叔叔\N{\fs16\fsp0}Michael, keep an eye on the sauce. Stay here with your Uncle Michael.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.62,1:57:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我请麦可注意配料  我和凯伦就出去了\N{\fs16\fsp0}So I asked my brother to watch the sauce, and Karen and I started out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.29,1:57:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天呀  我看见了\N{\fs16\fsp0}Oh, God. I see it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.63,1:57:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我看见了  就在那儿  - 该死\N{\fs16\fsp0}- I see it. Look, it's right there. - Damn!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.33,1:57:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就是它  - 就在那边\N{\fs16\fsp0}- That's it. - There it is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.93,1:57:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去你妈妈家\N{\fs16\fsp0}We got to get to your mother's.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.17,1:57:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看见了吧  我告诉你了嘛\N{\fs16\fsp0}See, I told you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.63,1:57:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很奇怪\N{\fs16\fsp0}It's funny.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.40,1:57:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但并不是世界末日  - 我们先去你妈妈家\N{\fs16\fsp0}- It's not the end of the world. - We're going to your mother's.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.93,1:58:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进去告诉你妈妈  外面的东西不要碰  好吗\N{\fs16\fsp0}Go inside, tell your mother not to touch anything outside the house. Nothing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.87,1:58:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不到你妈妈家去  非要到我妈家来\N{\fs16\fsp0}We couldn't go to your mother's house? You had to come here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.11,1:58:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来  去购物吧\N{\fs16\fsp0}Let's go shopping.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.02,1:58:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有  我没疯  这死东西跟了我一早上\N{\fs16\fsp0}I'm not nuts, it's been following me all morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.90,1:58:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}中午12点30分
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.76,1:58:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你讲啦\N{\fs16\fsp0}I'm telling you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.42,1:58:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  好啦  他说我疑心病太重\N{\fs16\fsp0}Fine. Fine. He thinks I'm paranoid!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.76,1:58:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该把直升机带到他那  看我是不是疑心病\N{\fs16\fsp0}I should bring him the helicopter, then we'll see how paranoid I am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.17,1:58:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们进去吧\N{\fs16\fsp0}Come on, let's go inside.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.57,1:58:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下午1点30分
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.14,1:58:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不见了\N{\fs16\fsp0}Yeah, it's gone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.57,1:58:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我听不见声音了  -来吧  回你妈妈家\N{\fs16\fsp0}- I don't hear anything. - Let's go back to your mother's.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.18,1:58:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下午3点30分
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.42,1:59:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 还可以吗  - 太好了  太好了\N{\fs16\fsp0}- They all right? - Beautiful. They're great.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.83,1:59:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了  你是疑心病吗  我告诉你  他是多心罢了\N{\fs16\fsp0}Didn't I tell you, you were paranoid? Didn't I tell him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.66,1:59:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  我需要吸一口\N{\fs16\fsp0}Yeah. I need a hit.{\r}
